      "content": "thanks for the tip. you mentioned nitrogen... is that why it's just the bottom leaves getting hit? it feels like something is actually stealing the nutrients before they can get to the rest of the plant. how do i know if it's actually a deficiency or if something in the soil is just blocking it?",
